{"tid":197084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人戴咗帽嘅你唔該入一入嚟。。","createTime":"2017-04-11T16:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T01:25:08.000Z","uid":79940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81c2098499548904c96d65c32e5427e12a88b952","tid":197084,"uid":79940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n條女講分手都過咗一排<br />\n一直同我話唔係我同佢問題，係因為遠距離<br />\n點知最近先知原來自己應該好早就戴咗帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都覺得佢係雞係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但仲未放得低。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如大家又分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85de27c4b00edc0cd736df50014f23d381812f35","tid":197084,"uid":79940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:35:30.000Z","msg":"sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"02920ca2dbff2ee09c740e09bf7aaef38bb6a656","tid":197084,"uid":88521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"佢去台灣第一日識左個香港男仔<br />\n2個星期同左佢一齊同我講分手<br />\n利申 同佢拍左3年"},{"pid":"41e7b71efe6c5856729189b06f3f11ba5683cbd2","tid":197084,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"感情啲野 邊個認真邊個輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d0e20fcd05e272d7947ffd0f132fb4bef1ec86","tid":197084,"uid":15182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"同佢講他朝君體也相同"},{"pid":"e3cebdf51c483119644e7ffef0896a3daf3cbc5c","tid":197084,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"雞黎"},{"pid":"bf1613c8f34919351ffd30112b3e0ced9f5454c4","tid":197084,"uid":102190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e084a138c33265d087c6db934dee567ad47a21","tid":197084,"uid":72276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d9f43f466f5f7f57e2021752ffb55c6671d560","tid":197084,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:19:52.000Z","msg":"戴過兩年，哈哈哈哈 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952ccd9df05f22c3966ead763c14afaf5521abaa","tid":197084,"uid":70079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T23:55:45.000Z","msg":"係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe0cd781e9a8e62c59409896b3f2b2fabc482c1","tid":197084,"uid":64798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:14:57.000Z","msg":"帽咪帽，有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>執著</strong>只係你仲未識玩呢個遊戲"},{"pid":"10e2a9713452657d3945c309a83bb15183bfbae3","tid":197084,"uid":79940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴過兩年，哈哈哈哈 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore"},{"pid":"8f76a6b3559f210d2818fd34b52d6319704f1bb8","tid":197084,"uid":79940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帽咪帽，有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>執著</strong>只係你仲未識玩呢個遊戲</blockquote><br />\n真正愛過邊有咁易？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2776fe3ba5a6997f244b40796aa2a940f8624c","tid":197084,"uid":87000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"拍左超過4年 但唔知由幾時開始戴...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e702170da807f61c206ce9a5a404943e128eab","tid":197084,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戴過兩年，哈哈哈哈 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nex當年有好多難關、意外令佢唔開心，我盡哂力開解但佢寧願收埋，我幫佢、陪住佢過哂啲難關，但就係某一個難關既時候，俾個mk仔溝走左<br />\n<br />\n因為我份人比較理性，遇到難題主張處理，所以我想幫佢一齊面對，結果佢次次都揀逃避，然後就俾個靜係識玩既mk撬走左<br />\n<br />\n我知哂佢所有負面野，幫過佢全家計埋佢成三代人，出錢出力出人脈，差唔多十萬，大部分係借。佢話搵工，我一個老細+兩個高層俾佢揀是但一個，都算係筍工黎，基本上見工鳩見就得，因為係我介紹<br />\n<br />\n不過冇諗過我做到咁，竟然戴左兩年帽，仲要俾佢完全收埋<br />\n<br />\n其實我冇恨佢，經一事，長一智姐，只係非常十分難過，就算講起件事果陣幾平靜都好，都會不自覺流淚，講得耐仲會頭暈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得自己好撚冇用，俾mk搶，唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d12008a9115ff19a143c9786d6677fb9731423","tid":197084,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帽咪帽，有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>執著</strong>只係你仲未識玩呢個遊戲</blockquote><br />\n真正愛過邊有咁易？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實巴打係講得岩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛還愛，你唔可以無左理智"},{"pid":"817e19960f2adbbc66c12d19fe072086a756231a","tid":197084,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"照下鏡先啦"}]}